RDIAS SUPRAVENTRICULARES (TSV)","guid":"94E3-w6LQcyl7fLwwNiY4g","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia por reentrada nodal (TRNAV) → MAS FRECUENTE","guid":"8eqI6UWfT9KxQ4Eq2oKV8w","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia por via accesoria (TRAV)","guid":"0y0XPg6qT2aAd5miXhgXcw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"Taquicardia auricular","guid":"SkfDE7oYRqy8ie68rFlc8w","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"Manejo escalonado","guid":"3ImFavYSSKi7mKVX79q6Zg","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Maniobras vagales → primer paso","guid":"YizThBzkQt21uBQ2EL-3XQ","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Valsalva modificado (mayor tasa de exito)","guid":"gI7YLESaT5mfSGSUKDasjA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Masaje carotideo (precaucion en AM → soplo?)","guid":"nKaNmfyXTLu14QwuH9QXrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"Adenosina IV","guid":"6PlNngHsT5yeeXeIVOYIjg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"6 mg IV push rapido + flush","guid":"P0DNtEE1RwC2sD9b52_weA","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Si no responde → 12 mg IV","guid":"QbZHdD27QQGDy6N_y2mXww","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"Vida media ultracorta (6-10 seg)","guid":"8noAzJ-nQrOON5rqcc7CWw","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"Contraindicada en asma severa, WPW conocido","guid":"4tlfJ5ytRaiiNjx2M5J2_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"172","text":"Verapamilo 2.5-5 mg IV o diltiazem","guid":"ZzzoBeSzRQyPf7Oe2zFMoA","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"172","text":"Cardioversion sincronizada si refractaria o inestable","guid":"Z5UpxUW5R0aDl0nyMORstA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"TAQUICARDIAS VENTRICULARES (TV)","guid":"4DuSspswQ9iTSjXuQ0Zklw","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Clasificacion","guid":"Yz7PbT2FRiqDrIzqQR5GBw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"TV MONOMORFA → QRS uniforme","guid":"gsbmFoVzRyyry9ILPxvoZQ","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Sostenida (>30 seg o inestabilidad)","guid":"d485CeX1QdWy0AlGBmZ77w","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"No sostenida (<30 seg, autolimitada)","guid":"CCvslewlRXK4QP9Eib17qg","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"TV POLIMORFA → QRS variable","guid":"rtD4v0OzRmebd3C_wK52Gg","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Con QT normal → isquemia hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"x3Ili42sSVu4rBj9ufivdg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Con QT largo → Torsade de Pointes","guid":"NsAlMsiYSUeKllFI2l_Nug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"183","text":"Manejo TV monomorfa sostenida","guid":"93SNTRNwSAmHkWPM3TCQzw","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"INESTABLE → cardioversion sincronizada 100-200 J","guid":"a7V3GAiDQlOQGQzFZ9geNA","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"ESTABLE → farmacologico","guid":"lLMFWVe3T1-vuz5n2PEncQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"NNT TheNNT → Procainamida vs Amiodarona en TV estable","guid":"pB7R5Gw3RbyCeZ63Q6_9Ow","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Estudio PROCAMIO (Ortiz 2017, Eur Heart J)","guid":"Ebp8O6zuSKSQY4ihJKt4_w","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"74 pacientes con TV estable","guid":"2JG49SpgSGiQgnB2OvIyOA","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"Procainamida 10 mg/kg IV en 20 min","guid":"NaLEo-YaTUmJpoZiTCUvPA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"NNT 4 para conversion a ritmo basal","guid":"yj74Fe_0TeK74X-piufvIQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"194","text":"NNH 3 para eventos adversos cardiacos mayores con amiodarona","guid":"tRKXzFjbSVq61qZYw7O5VQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"194","text":"Recomendacion AMARILLA → evidencia debil pero mejor disponible","guid":"OxROV3dFRBaougDhsbn9ZA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"194","text":"AHA recomienda procainamida (IIa) sobre amiodarona (IIb)","guid":"q-Rbe7lhRZON54zvhHl9LQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"194","text":"PERLA → procainamida superior a amiodarona en TV estable","guid":"BWkaivDPSSGg8qE-DNSMHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"193","text":"Amiodarona 150 mg IV en 10 min → alternativa","guid":"7gQT4TcsTlyz-oEqJy4Dew","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"Luego infusion 1 mg/min x 6h → 0.5 mg/min x 18h","guid":"qKVGQnS-TXuRyRDTMNLjFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"193","text":"Lidocaina → rol limitado actualmente","guid":"YWci5BV6T0OSlPijRZW16w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"183","text":"Torsade de Pointes","guid":"WfpMgERjT8ClkUUxksaCbA","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"QT largo + TV polimorfa","guid":"Jph9yQWmQ56tAxrnrD5EgA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Causas → farmacos (antiarritmicos IA/III, macrolidos, antipsicóticos), hipoK, hipoMg","guid":"bt_LBM0ETuiglzq0fX8BeA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"Manejo → MgSO4 2 g IV en 2 min (primera linea)","guid":"z42l5ae2SDaa5ZrbUfolnQ","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Isoproterenol o marcapaso temporal (overdrive pacing)","guid":"maJZLv2aSIGgwdFA4pdtBQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"Cardioversion si inestable","guid":"NNGVs4rgTkqDJLqxW9MShw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"NO dar amiodarona (prolonga QT)","guid":"xaU7hibeTpepDJcYMnnwCw","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"206","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → causa frecuente: polifarmacia con farmacos que prolongan QT","guid":"B7CXIBcFR3KolR-F23U0Nw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"0","text":"BRADIARRITMIAS","guid":"4fy2Dj76SUa6ZyYKoZJjDQ","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Bradicardia sinusal","guid":"V8_hr7elR3CHrAB_LXHGgA","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"FC <60, puede ser fisiologica","guid":"bXHB1SVEToGpA_vmbuG_4A","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"Sintomatica si hipotension, sincope, IC","guid":"gZXm7f4AQG6fs6Ps8rt9QQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"Bloqueo AV","guid":"iXRBAJPFQwGEr4vcjdyU2w","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"1er grado → PR >200 ms, benigno","guid":"2YP9MPH7TPKKeWxTB_Jlzw","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"2do grado Mobitz I (Wenckebach) → generalmente benigno","guid":"JRKoZ9ZSQ_ucnTKZ72fzwA","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"2do grado Mobitz II → riesgo de progresion, considerar marcapaso","guid":"Am3G8A3BRKOAC7_cAN4ciQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"3er grado (completo) → emergencia, marcapaso","guid":"8hAKtg06Qf6qDj-gBFCckw","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"214","text":"Manejo bradicardia sintomatica","guid":"hm-FVqtpR-y8sFbq9uIsuw","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"Atropina 0.5-1 mg IV (puede repetir hasta 3 mg)","guid":"VIS2oCzKQ9iUBSvv31y-pA","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Inefectiva en BAV 3er grado infranodal","guid":"FBsHgkqkQy2H8g-LpQSLmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"Isoproterenol infusion 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"l02LlqRFSluaXRCaCmf8Xw","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"223","text":"Dopamina 5-20 mcg/kg/min","guid":"JxzOXTVfQdGC8nmgUPtDaw","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"223","text":"Adrenalina 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"qZlz5ludQeS2ZW7nDQtAKg","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"223","text":"Marcapaso transcutaneo → puente a transvenoso","guid":"fNprfO-nTCq1Wclbkpy4Eg","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"223","text":"Marcapaso transvenoso temporal → definitivo","guid":"K84bIJ-sSo-DjaUrAhz5eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"214","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"VqYhG1AURsK3jd7RdvhtHQ","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"Bradicardia frecuente por farmacos (betabloqueadores, digoxina, calcioantagonistas)","guid":"A8CA1ZBiShqCvU09WU2mwQ","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"Enfermedad del nodo sinusal","guid":"sltea6k-QKaH-g2Gk9YbXw","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"Degeneracion del sistema de conduccion","guid":"txTBsbFrTMKApIcnehnGnA","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"PERLA → siempre revisar farmacos antes de asumir bradicardia intrinseca","guid":"sUlGSbhpQwOo54L0N1AnUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIATRICAS TRANSVERSALES","guid":"t--Fog0iRuiJvfmNIO7Eew","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"Farmacocinetica alterada","guid":"SZ6BQ9ruR9uPSVotENUBsA","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Menor metabolismo hepatico → acumulacion amiodarona","guid":"OWgVYkpQS_OUib__2rM9Dg","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"Menor filtracion glomerular → ajustar digoxina, DOACs","guid":"j3f_TD8aSHi6mH6UZrWXJw","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"237","text":"Mayor sensibilidad a farmacos cronotropos negativos","guid":"egiU4mBCRtyDtQ3-FNzlzA","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"237","text":"Menor masa muscular → creatinina falsamente normal","guid":"4ZLnBw_FTEWA8eSfd3jzMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"236","text":"Comorbilidades","guid":"r_wJI4vGR7Wcxc10aG8bMA","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"IC + FA → combinacion frecuente en AM","guid":"CENguj14Qg63ctbNG0yUbg","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"ERC → ajustar anticoagulacion","guid":"sBzsCvwWRDGjUlHh8yxtqw","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"Caidas → evaluar riesgo antes de anticoagular (HAS-BLED no es razon para no ACO)","guid":"v5oBjGGVTY6kkHKrAu0lfg","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"242","text":"Fragilidad → individualizar metas","guid":"o5CTbePQRV2uukmdbYao9w","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"242","text":"Demencia → adherencia farmacologica comprometida","guid":"_wX8oxIFReK4TfhOnybrOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"236","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"XLQqVSbdRuu-aeYDsy-rOA","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"Interacciones con anticoagulantes","guid":"RYN33ZRoSnacaHFl8YAUDw","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"Farmacos que prolongan QT → lista larga en AM","guid":"K0TmB0Q2TDycObocHBlbBA","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"Antipsicóticos, antidepresivos, macrolidos, quinolonas, ondansetron","guid":"6nEpG7M6Q8OiFC9mjT_aVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"Carga anticolinergica de algunos antiarritmicos","guid":"eq2bOxAfQFGNBwHVeNe3fQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"236","text":"Decisiones de proporcionalidad","guid":"PpJ5OHI2R0iCaKlColieDQ","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"FA permanente en AM muy fragil → solo control FC, no anticoagular si riesgo > beneficio","guid":"JoTwm1RuRKWrjUl6cO5Kvw","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"Considerar directivas anticipadas","guid":"nga7DhRrTtStcci913TqPQ","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"Calidad de vida sobre longevidad en decisiones","guid":"2Y8oVHwaQL2DY3neiZol3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO RESUMEN FA EN URGENCIA","guid":"iE6onAA2TFKbimX5AJxTeg","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"PASO 1 → Confirmar FA (ECG) + evaluar estabilidad","guid":"dUiZ-NbfROa8-27Cyn-IUg","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"PASO 2 → Inestable → cardioversion electrica sincronizada","guid":"TY9n-CkNRrKNWnbd6sTbxg","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"PASO 3 → Estable → control de frecuencia (betabloqueador o calcioantagonista)","guid":"2IOk-E1PS9KG0oj7S6T-0Q","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"PASO 4 → Buscar causa (infeccion, IC, TEP, tiroides, electrolitos)","guid":"XVu3Sj48RFWLRHl3VA3MQA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"257","text":"PASO 5 → Evaluar necesidad de cardioversion vs mantener control FC","guid":"-bNl07TFRYuIQ27Kugc9Zw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"257","text":"PASO 6 → Anticoagulacion segun CHA2DS2-VASc","guid":"SdMNpQxlSuOBrk7foz6Tog","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO RESUMEN TAQUICARDIA QRS ANCHO","guid":"SMuAQUOMSpC-PPKfuCYnmg","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"Regular + monomorfa → TV monomorfa → procainamida o cardioversion","guid":"N9UY15vpQ5i-YJ_pf2-Ntw","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"Regular + polimorfa + QT largo → Torsade → MgSO4","guid":"sIYahhcwS56eipQlmAGiNQ","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"264","text":"Irregular + QRS ancho → FA preexcitada (WPW) → procainamida o cardioversion, NO frenadores NAV","guid":"BB247_IaSeiXt9dQDVBnWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"G0zLqcJqTd6MayME-2obQQ","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"4U7FzlEUQu65ueRoicUFOg","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Pulso irregularmente irregular (palpacion medica) -> LR+ 4.5 -> LR- 0.16 -> PMID:16536961","guid":"XyglKUo0SqC3PpsGUvjDWw","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"Auscultacion cardiaca irregular -> LR+ 4.2 -> LR- 0.2 -> PMID:17673732 (SAFE)","guid":"mAAZ81GpSDGqOL848gyoQg","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"Pulso irregular detectado por paciente -> LR+ 1.9 -> LR- NR -> PMID:16536961","guid":"0jyx_D2wTVyBWMYpX3mp_A","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"269","text":"Deficit de pulso (apical > radial) -> [descriptivo clasico, LR no consolidado]","guid":"PkNvURXHSFGKE5hvR7lvKg","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"269","text":"Palpitaciones + mareo -> sintoma comun, no LR especifico","guid":"Fo8NgMHNRf24vwJFL0bL2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"268","text":"HALLAZGOS ECG","guid":"DbeFMmrQQfGFPBaD1LQ0-A","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"ECG 12 derivaciones (gold standard) -> LR+ muy alto -> (definitorio)","guid":"d5eL2RDcRFugH4A5mvGR3w","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"Ausencia de onda P + R-R irregular -> [definitorio FA]","guid":"rG5wt3-yRAG5WjRCyluIgg","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"Taquicardia irregular QRS angosto -> FA vs taquicardia atrial multifocal","guid":"sI6QNZMNQaegwemmig44nA","children":[]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"268","text":"DISPOSITIVOS","guid":"WHnW4XEzRyWM4apKDMuSZQ","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"Single-lead ECG (AliveCor, Apple Watch, KardiaMobile) -> LR+ ~30-100 -> LR- ~0.02 -> PMID:24687081","guid":"JsMRaCYGTLKlBHjhb9XbXg","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"Oximetria de pulso con deteccion FA -> LR+ 8.4 -> LR- 0.2 -> PMID:29562087","guid":"rsloe4fFSTSuxzEi95c2cg","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"279","text":"Holter 24-48h (FA paroxistica) -> variable por duracion monitoreo","guid":"LklXjFGwTwOnHp8NPkzHJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"268","text":"SCORE / REGLA CLINICA (riesgo embolico)","guid":"M-bFkw-YQTeoIMDwatQbzw","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"CHA2DS2-VASc >=2 (hombres) o >=3 (mujeres) -> indicacion anticoagulacion","guid":"un_B5gi5QK63KlS_2qynyA","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"283","text":"HAS-BLED >=3 -> alto riesgo sangrado, no contraindica AC sino intensifica monitoreo","guid":"6wCSZosqSru58N3f0gJkKw","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"283","text":"EHRA >=IIa -> indicacion control ritmo","guid":"z9Ey80HZTqCcXe62GX--TA","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"268","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"YcQgBpLzT5ao5Jrw0fmsTA","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE (single-lead ECG con algoritmo)","guid":"5-42G2dTT06hbDOm7G4HKw","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"LR+ 2-5 -> cambio moderado (palpacion pulso irregular)","guid":"8mZ03DYjSQqN4OkvbTsOOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"268","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"4sHhAEEiSeGM1-ggxTQ59g","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"Prevalencia >10 porciento en >80 anos","guid":"6UG-EYBzR0-nSDHLM4qnjA","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"290","text":"Fragilidad y riesgo de caidas NO son contraindicaciones absolutas a anticoagulacion","guid":"066DiW-TSxe8YW--Hirfpw","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"290","text":"Ajuste DOACs por edad, peso, creatinina (Apixaban criterios 2/3: >=80a, <=60kg, Cr >=1.5)","guid":"xUW3WH8OTdK1uNZC3tGU9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"nPdq36qoT6eS0y8v1hu6hg","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"FA es la arritmia sostenida mas comun en\\Nadulto mayor; prevalencia 8-10% en >75 anos.","guid":"REFk1sijTWWNZ3yXAnU-2Q","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"ESC 2024: control de ritmo precoz mejora\\Npronostico vs control de frecuencia (EAST-AFNET 4).","guid":"yaET0ybgR7qZUan9KO14FA","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"Estrategia AF-CARE (ESC 2024): C-Comorbilidades,\\NA-Avoid stroke, R-Reduce symptoms, E-Evaluation.","guid":"AYa4UmzvTmeEkYlCDsUgFw","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"CHA2DS2-VA (sin sexo) reemplaza a CHA2DS2-VASc\\Nen ESC 2024.","guid":"CiYqjFp0TxuGSGay6F3Bgw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"294","text":"DOACs preferidos sobre warfarina en FA no valvular,\\Nincluso en adulto mayor (NEJM meta-analisis).","guid":"R-Wn5TjDRsyaTucowkiZFw","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"294","text":"Apixaban dosis reducida 2.5 mg c/12 h:\\N≥2 de 3 criterios (≥80a, ≤60kg, Cr ≥1.5 mg/dL).","guid":"ZpsEfCJJREWR4sUl6bM2Eg","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"294","text":"Fragilidad y riesgo de caidas NO son contraindicaciones\\Nabsolutas a anticoagulacion (riesgo HIC <1% sin anticoag\\Nvs beneficio prevencion ACV).","guid":"1SwljvG2RQuXqVqiP9DgQw","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"294","text":"Cardioversion electrica >48 h sin anticoag\\N→ ETE previo o anticoag 3 sem antes + 4 sem despues.","guid":"s64w1EQkSOGyxSTp9xcQPw","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"294","text":"MgSO4 2g IV en FA con RVR: control adicional\\N(NNT bajo segun TheNNT.com).","guid":"IYpU05XLQr-1OVoAhbyJrg","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"294","text":"Procainamida superior a amiodarona en TV\\Nestable (PROCAMIO).","guid":"C3kYQNNISzi88-oZDptC6A","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"294","text":"Digoxina util cuando betabloqueadores\\Ncontraindicados (asma severa, BAV).","guid":"7EUVxuDxQDCNvQ3y4iHNTA","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"294","text":"FA en AM frecuentemente asintomatica\\N→ tamizaje activo con ECG/Holter en >65a.","guid":"9Pba66kWSTmDVUJKNFRJgA","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"294","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"gFUz95ZmSJ6TnjzBBdr4DA","children":[{"id":"308","parent":"307","text":"ESC 2024 → guia manejo FA","guid":"GOz93c3YRpuR6Jr8oPAcyA","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"307","text":"RACE II → control lenient vs estricto (Van Gelder 2010, PMID:20231232)","guid":"gc4z-daYTnCxNPB0p6qONw","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"307","text":"PROCAMIO → procainamida vs amiodarona en TV estable (Ortiz 2017, PMID:28025219)","guid":"s7VPvumRTKazQQYKJfQTEA","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"307","text":"ARISTOTLE → apixaban vs warfarina en FA (Granger 2011, PMID:21870978)","guid":"sUCAAyq7SqWterQsOVp6Dg","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"307","text":"RE-LY → dabigatran vs warfarina (Connolly 2009, PMID:19717844)","guid":"P_A3ZoQKTm-UpIOb4QP_uw","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"307","text":"AFFIRM → ritmo vs frecuencia en FA (Wyse 2002, PMID:12466507)","guid":"C4uxuoBMQAup3sHbevmyGQ","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"307","text":"TheNNT.com → NNT de MgSO4 IV en FA+RVR, procainamida vs amiodarona en TV","guid":"HOTovi0FQPWZI-465jJghA","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"307","text":"Kirchhof 2016 → ESC guidelines AF (PMID:27567408)","guid":"Kc-MCX3lS2ey07yNw6a8AQ","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"307","text":"January 2014 → AHA/ACC guideline AF (PMID:24682347)","guid":"mPEZ5Kk2ScKSLbjed9vMZg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":316,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Cuidados-Domicilio","filename":"04-Cuidados-Especiales-Contexto-Social","id":"map_100","resolved_references":[]}